  "title": "The Running of \u03b1_EM in Integer Arithmetic",
  "upload_type": "publication",
  "publication_type": "article",
  "description": "The QED running of the electromagnetic coupling constant \u03b1_EM from the Z boson mass to atomic scale is computed in exact rational arithmetic. Every intermediate value is a ratio of two integers. Seven measured rationals enter the computation; all transcendentals (\u03c0, ln) are represented as exact integer pairs at 100+ digit precision via [@HOWL-MATH-2-2026]. The result \u2014 1/\u03b1_EM = 137.0360025 \u2014 matches CODATA 2022 (137.0359992) to 0.02 parts per million.",
